    <summary>A fully featured text and code editor</summary>
    <description>Twistpad is a fully featured text and code editor for Windows. Twistpad can be used as a simple notepad replacer or a featured packed editor targeting web and software developers. Twistpad supports a full range of syntax highlighting (colored keywords) for the most popular formats out of the box (HTML, ASP, XML, C++, Java, Pascal, etc) but it's strength relies on the easy to create new highlighting schemes.

This version is provided as freeware only for personal, non-commercial use. **THE USE OF THE FREE EDITION FOR BUSINESS OR COMMERCIAL PURPOSES IS PROHIBITED.** Home users, Open Source contributors, students, hobbyists and charity or humanitarian organizations can use the FREE EDITION for non-commercial activity **ONLY**.

Written in native code (32 bit only for free edition), you can be sure that no system files are altered or large additional run-time libraries are required. Performance is also something we had in mind when designing Twistpad, so fast start up time and fast text parsing are guaranteed.

## Features
* [Syntax Highlight](https://www.carthagosoft.net/TwistpadSyn.php)
* Unicode support
* Modern Windows editions support
* High DPI support
* Integrated file compare
* Tabbed interface
* Multiple clipboard support
* Integrated file browser
* Itegrated file history
* Search and replace in text files
* Editor themes support
* Enhanced file switch
* Function list
* Bookmarks
* External tool support
* Block selection
* Print and Print Preview
* Plug-in support
* Text Snippets
* Track changes
* Templates
* Auto complete
* Formatting text tools
* Document bar
* Customization options
* Guidelines and code helpers
* Transparent selection
* Binary file warning
* Tool Windows
* File Changed
* Application themes
* Export Syntax Highlight

